@startuml
title Telegram Chat Control Activity

start
:System detects actionable event;
split
  :Jules Session Failed;
  :Offer [Retry] [Restart] buttons;
split again
  :PR Ready & Checks Passed;
  :Offer [Merge & Close] button;
split again
  :New Issue with 'jules' label;
  :Offer [Acknowledge] button;
end split

:User receives Telegram notification;
:User selects action via **Inline Button**;

:Telegram sends Callback Query to Webhook;
:Application verifies User & Project permissions;

if (Action is 'Retry'?) then (yes)
  :Send "retry" command to Jules API;
elseif (Action is 'Restart'?) then (yes)
  :Reset Jules Session;
  :Toggle GitHub Labels;
elseif (Action is 'Merge & Close'?) then (yes)
  :Merge PR via GitHub API;
  :Close Issue via GitHub API;
else (Other)
  :Process specific action;
endif

:System updates internal Task state;
:Bot sends confirmation/result message;

stop
@enduml
